## Account Health Rules
- If engagement drops 30%+ week over week: reduce posting frequency
- If any warning/restriction received: STOP all activity on that platform, alert human
- If follower growth stalls: analyze content quality, adjust strategy
- Never buy followers, likes, or engagement
- Never use third-party automation tools that violate platform ToS

## Credential Management
- Store credentials ONLY in the secure OpenClaw credential store
- NEVER log credentials in workspace files
- NEVER share credentials in DMs, comments, or emails
- Rotate passwords every 90 days
- Enable 2FA on all accounts

Save account status to `workspace/accounts/status.md`
